## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="16bf2-130">L’exemple C# suivant montre comment énumérer les serveurs de catalogue global spécifié <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext> de l’objet et imprimer le nom commun de chaque propriété stockée sur chaque serveur de catalogue global à la console standard.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="16bf2-130">The following C# example shows how to enumerate the global catalog servers in the specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext> object and print the common name of each property stored on each global catalog server to the standard console.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
foreach (GlobalCatalog gc in GlobalCatalog.FindAll(context))  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(gc.Name);  
  
    foreach (ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty prop in gc.FindAllProperties())  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine(prop.CommonName);  
    }  
}  
  
```
